---
title: Tunisian Freekeh Stew with Roasted Chickpeas and Greek Yogurt
description: Grains like freekeh usually act as a starchy side to proteins and veggies and are rarely the star of the show. In this stew, however, we’re putting it front and center. It adds exciting texture and heft to each spoonful. Roasted chickpeas and a medley of chopped veggies keep things hearty, while our Tunisian spice blend adds an enchanting perfume.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tunisian-freekeh-stew-14408a62.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/tunisian-freekeh-stew-f709e7ec.pdf
time required: 45 minutes
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/tunisian-freekeh-stew-58580c0fa28e1a36247c2902
cuisine: African
nutrition:
  calories: 757 kcal
  fat: 21 g
  saturated fat: 2 g
  carbohydrates: 109 g
